content: Ultimately I don't understand a thing, I try to do the best I can, I know you try to do the same. We're just so bound to make mistakes, you could call it a disposition, I apologize for all your tears, I wish I could be different. But I'm still growing up, into the one you can call your love. I don't know if I'll ever be enough. I'm throwing in my chips, I guess I tend to push my luck.
author: Khai Dreams
